sections.History:
===[[Season 1]]===

House Caron takes part in the Tourney of the Hand.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[The Wolf and the Lion]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 2]]===

Like most of the Stormlords, House Caron pledges its support to [[Renly Baratheon]]'s claim to the [[Iron Throne]]. Following the [[Assassination of Renly I|death]] of Renly, the Carons go over to [[Stannis Baratheon|Stannis]] and participate in the [[Battle of the Blackwater]].&lt;ref&gt;Season 2 Bluray: War of the Five Kings feature&lt;/ref&gt;
